	<key>readme</key>
	<string>## Usage
The workflow offers three [hotkeys](https://www.alfredapp.com/help/workflows/triggers/hotkey/):

1. Autocorrect the word under the cursor.
2. Suggest synonyms for the word under the cursor.
3. Rephrase the selected text via ChatGPT, improving its language (requires OpenAI API key). There are 3 formatting options:
	+ Plain: just output the changed text.
	+ Markdown: Additions are displayed as `==highlights==`, deletions are displayed as `~~strikethroughs~~`.
	+ [Critic Markup](https://github.com/CriticMarkup/CriticMarkup-toolkit).

---

Created by [Chris Grieser](https://chris-grieser.de/).</string>
